Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:40.00,0:01:42.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,葵大小姐 为什么你要这么做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.35,0:01:53.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,葵…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.48,0:01:58.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第4话  同棲（同居）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.33,0:02:07.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.63,0:02:10.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也要离开樱庭家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.86,0:02:11.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,即使舍弃一切
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.47,0:02:13.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也想要和薰在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.70,0:02:16.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以拜托你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.94,0:02:20.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,让我以薰的妻子的身份 跟您缔结婚约吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.74,0:02:24.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,该怎么办…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.24,0:02:27.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不经大脑就说出这种话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.71,0:02:31.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薰他会怎么想呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.85,0:02:35.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,会不会认为我是个冒失的女人呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.42,0:02:41.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是我从很久以前就下定决心要当薰的妻子了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.36,0:02:45.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把身心都献给薰…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.57,0:02:55.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,身心都…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.04,0:02:57.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没问题吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.98,0:03:07.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薰他会接受我吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.46,0:03:20.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯 加油
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.03,0:03:23.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为我就将是薰的妻子了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.48,0:03:31.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薰？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.82,0:03:46.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那个…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.83,0:03:48.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薰？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.00,0:03:52.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薰？薰？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.67,0:03:55.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.27,0:03:57.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抱歉…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.67,0:03:58.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,突然有点晕…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.71,0:04:01.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,烧的好厉害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.71,0:04:02.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.11,0:04:05.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没问题的啦…你看…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.58,0:04:07.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没问题…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.25,0:04:11.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薰？薰！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.60,0:04:23.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,谢谢你 小葵…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.93,0:04:26.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是我的错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.47,0:04:33.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起… 都是为了我薰才会…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.31,0:04:35.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没这回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.31,0:04:37.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要有小葵在我身边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.14,0:04:40.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我就会很安心 很高兴了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.72,0:04:44.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薰…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.99,0:04:51.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,来 我来帮你擦汗 就这样不要动喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.99,0:04:54.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不用了 我自己来就好…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.66,0:04:58.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请不要这样说 就让我来做吧 薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.14,0:05:10.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抱歉 让你看到 这种让人不舒服的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.95,0:05:18.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小葵…？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.85,0:05:23.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薰的伤痕 就让我用时间来治好它吧…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.92,0:05:27.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请让我一直陪在你的身边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.19,0:05:30.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我绝对不会离开你的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.17,0:05:36.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯 谢谢你 小葵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.51,0:05:47.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薰 你很冷吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.91,0:05:49.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯…有点…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.62,0:05:55.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薰 你能够稍微把脸往别的地方看一下吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.74,0:06:17.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊 小葵…？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.51,0:06:19.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可以 薰！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.95,0:06:21.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请不要看这边…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.05,0:06:23.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抱…抱歉…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.52,0:06:26.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我只能做到这点事情…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.49,0:06:34.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,暖和吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.13,0:06:38.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小葵的体温传过来了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.43,0:06:41.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,听到可薰的心跳声了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.68,0:06:57.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薰 身体状况怎么样了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.92,0:07:00.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,差不多都好了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.73,0:07:08.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太好了 烧好像都退了的样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.76,0:07:10.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,吓了我一跳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.43,0:07:13.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你怎么了吗？薰？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.90,0:07:18.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不 这都是多亏小葵用身体照顾我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.11,0:07:21.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用身体…？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.98,0:07:23.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊 所以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.44,0:07:25.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那之后我们两个很快就睡着了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.48,0:07:27.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以感冒才很快就好了啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.62,0:07:32.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薰你真是的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.45,0:07:35.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你就再稍微躺一下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.86,0:07:41.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好可爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.16,0:07:44.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,难道这就是新婚的气氛吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.30,0:07:47.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么了吗？小葵？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.31,0:07:58.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你果然在这里啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.98,0:07:59.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妈妈…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.81,0:08:01.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妈妈？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.78,0:08:05.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,葵 这是怎么一回事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.79,0:08:11.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你到底在想些什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.19,0:08:14.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也不听雅的话乖乖回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.03,0:08:20.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟花菱家的婚约早就已经取消了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.30,0:08:26.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这不像是平常的葵…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.21,0:08:32.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你现在到底在想什么？向我说明一下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.91,0:08:36.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小葵…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.92,0:08:38.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不管怎样…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.98,0:08:39.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,葵大小姐…？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.09,0:08:43.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不管怎样都忘不了薰的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.92,0:08:46.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没说一声就擅自离家让大家担心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.43,0:08:47.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是真的有在反省
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.03,0:08:48.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,既然这样…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.96,0:08:50.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.40,0:08:52.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,来到了这里我知道了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.43,0:08:56.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我以前过的生活被照顾的太无微不至了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.74,0:09:01.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要再次感谢爸爸妈妈…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.04,0:09:04.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.21,0:09:07.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是我在这里找到了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.18,0:09:10.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我绝对不能放手的最重要的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.38,0:09:11.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最重要的东西？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.05,0:09:17.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是陪在薰的身边…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.89,0:09:19.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,照顾着薰…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.36,0:09:22.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟薰一起生活…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.74,0:09:41.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我在这里找到了身为薰妻子的幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.58,0:09:43.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在说什么啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.42,0:09:46.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,葵大小姐是樱庭家的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.43,0:09:58.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,本来是那么顺从、柔弱的孩子…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.18,0:10:15.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,葵大小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.48,0:10:18.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们回去吧 雅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.32,0:10:20.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太太？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.45,0:10:21.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,葵 你也一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.89,0:10:23.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妈妈 我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.82,0:10:26.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你这样子会有点不方便吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.56,0:10:30.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,先回家一趟好好准备一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.00,0:10:33.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,开始你的新生活吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.70,0:10:37.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你父亲那边我会帮你解释的 你放心吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.51,0:10:40.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妈妈 那么说…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.94,0:10:44.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,葵 你真的长大了呢…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.35,0:10:47.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妈妈…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.57,0:11:10.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薰！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.51,0:11:17.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我回来了 薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.11,0:11:19.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,欢迎回来 小葵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.33,0:11:36.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.46,0:11:37.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我脸上有什么东西吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.10,0:11:40.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为我有好一阵子没看到薰的脸可嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.77,0:11:47.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,终于能够在一起了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.61,0:11:52.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是房间只有六块榻榻米大 可能会很幸苦喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.01,0:11:56.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不会 因为我有薰啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.35,0:11:57.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要这样就足够了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.93,0:12:08.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,空了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.33,0:12:10.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.43,0:12:13.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薰 这到底是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.53,0:12:15.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,让您久等了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.91,0:12:21.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雅？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.11,0:12:31.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是樱庭家所拥有的别墅之一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.45,0:12:33.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有一段时间没有使用了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.12,0:12:37.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,从今天开始就把这里当作新居来使用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.23,0:12:41.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好棒的洋房喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.40,0:12:43.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要您喜欢就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.86,0:12:48.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我以前就想来这种洋房住一次看看了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.84,0:12:50.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真令人有点兴奋呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.54,0:12:55.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薰少爷的行李已经搬到那里去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.51,0:12:57.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那里？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.18,0:13:06.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那个 真的在这里吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.85,0:13:08.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请多多少少忍耐一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.32,0:13:11.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是为了避免樱庭家发生丑闻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.06,0:13:13.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,丑闻？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.63,0:13:16.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的 一个跟花菱家断绝关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.00,0:13:20.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和樱庭家毫无关系的人变成了继承者的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.83,0:13:23.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,内部一定会出现反对的人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.90,0:13:26.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那样子樱庭集团就会四分五裂了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.61,0:13:30.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以这种事不能让外面的人知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.38,0:13:32.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请注意你们各种轻浮的言行举止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.61,0:13:34.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.01,0:13:37.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果是这样的话也没办法了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.52,0:13:41.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还有 我回来管理你们生活上的一切
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.52,0:13:43.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那样的话…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.86,0:13:45.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雅也要一起住？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.03,0:13:47.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽然说你可以跟葵大小姐在一起了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.29,0:13:49.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是可没有说你们两个可以独处喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.23,0:13:51.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,说…说的也是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.13,0:13:56.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,总而言之 我今后说的话你们绝对要服从
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.14,0:13:58.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.50,0:13:59.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊 是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.98,0:14:05.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么跟期待中的生活有点差距啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.81,0:14:10.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那差不多该来准备新居的事情了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.02,0:14:12.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对吧 薰？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.19,0:14:15.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对啊 那首先…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.66,0:14:18.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薰少爷还有这边的工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.56,0:14:20.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊 等一下啊 雅…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.36,0:14:22.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那个…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.07,0:14:37.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,餐厅的每个角落都要请你用抹布擦干净喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.88,0:14:42.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哎呀哎呀…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.32,0:14:48.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,像那种地方果然还是要男性才行吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.49,0:14:52.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊 要掉下去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.33,0:14:54.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请小心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.43,0:14:57.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,…这些全部都要搬吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.06,0:14:59.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这些都是长时间没有使用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.27,0:15:03.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,堆积下来不太好处理的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.61,0:15:10.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样子一点力气都没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.21,0:15:13.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要是葵大小姐发生什么事的话要怎么办呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.88,0:15:16.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可恶！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.92,0:15:22.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是个笨男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.59,0:15:24.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算葵大小姐选了这个男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.26,0:15:27.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也绝对不会认同他的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.53,0:15:30.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好热…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.36,0:15:33.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么了吗？雅？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.63,0:15:35.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,脸好红喔 是感冒吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.84,0:15:37.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么事都没有…！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.01,0:15:42.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,危险！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.31,0:15:44.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.55,0:15:49.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.65,0:15:53.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你这个禽兽！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.06,0:15:58.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么会变成这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.63,0:16:01.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,都还没开始整理自己的房间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.00,0:16:07.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,新生活的第一天却…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.50,0:16:11.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊 薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.31,0:16:14.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,房间马上就整理好了喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.21,0:16:16.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不用了啦 小葵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.64,0:16:17.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,之后我来做就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.31,0:16:21.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这点事情我还做的到啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.45,0:16:29.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我一直都在梦想着能够这样…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.66,0:16:32.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没想到就这样实现了 真的很高兴…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.56,0:16:33.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,梦想？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.89,0:16:38.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯 跟薰一起打扫 一起去买东西…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.90,0:16:40.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,帮忙做料理…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.20,0:16:42.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,两个人一起…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.20,0:16:45.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,从原点开始 一点一点的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.04,0:16:50.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,像这样子过自己的新生活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.85,0:16:54.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小葵…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.52,0:16:58.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯 今后就一起来做吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.35,0:17:00.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薰…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.26,0:17:15.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是不是对葵大小姐太过严格了呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.34,0:17:18.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我一直都在为葵大小姐着想 到了现在…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.57,0:17:20.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,却…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.74,0:17:26.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,像那样子有精神的笑容我连一次都没有看过…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.21,0:17:30.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,花菱…薰…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.67,0:17:50.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雅？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.14,0:17:52.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,葵大小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.74,0:17:54.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,非常抱歉 发出那么不成体统的声音…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.78,0:17:58.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,刚刚的那是什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.58,0:18:01.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像有什么在的样子…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.68,0:18:03.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么在？…小偷吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.38,0:18:06.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还是妖怪…幽灵？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.59,0:18:08.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎…怎么可能…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.80,0:18:17.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.33,0:18:20.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我去看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.10,0:18:22.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没关系的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.74,0:18:23.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薰…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.91,0:18:27.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,包在我身上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.48,0:18:30.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薰少爷？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.82,0:18:47.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薰？薰少爷？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.83,0:18:52.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,猫 猫…？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.33,0:18:54.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.20,0:18:56.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,它就是妖怪的真面目
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.57,0:19:00.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像在我们还没来之前就一直住在这里了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.34,0:19:04.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,突然吵吵闹闹的它就躲到这里来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.78,0:19:05.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原来是这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.65,0:19:08.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只不过是一只猫我就叫成这样…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.52,0:19:10.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是非常的丢脸…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.42,0:19:16.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.29,0:19:19.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那…那个 雅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.70,0:19:33.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,差不多该吃饭了吧 葵大小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.84,0:19:36.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薰少爷也一起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.41,0:19:41.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.27,0:20:05.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等一下啊 雅
